{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_vigil_set_1", "eventName": "未來將至", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "未來將至", "storyInfo": "萊昂圖索希望接受審判。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g3_srccourt", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "channel": "a", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖，今天的法庭可真熱鬧。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天的審判對一般市民開放，還會同步現場直播，湊熱鬧的人可太多了。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，我還是頭一次看到那些代表不同家族的陪審員到得如此整齊。這與其說是一場審判，不如說是一場新聞發佈會。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，今天站上法庭的，可是萊昂圖索·貝洛內。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西西里夫人下達了“家族不得介入新城市”的命令，卻沒有說她打算怎麼辦，所有人正摸不著頭腦呢。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，代表西西里夫人的法院終於有所動作了，當然萬眾矚目。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，審判他的可是那個拉維妮婭，她和貝洛內的關係可是眾所周知的。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝洛內都已經被除名了，她還能和貝洛內有什麼關係。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒不如說，她現在主動站出來審判萊昂圖索，就是急著想要和貝洛內撇清關係吧。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "加上西西里夫人明確出現在了這座城市，她這樣也是給自己名義上的主子作個秀。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是打得好算盤。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰知道呢。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，既然貝納爾多是那場混亂的主謀，他的兒子當然脫不了關係，今天的審判，應當會給我們一個答案。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得也是。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，法官來了。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "fadeout": "true", "randomness": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安靜。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想必有許多人對今天的審判感到不解。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是理所當然的事情，因為許多人只知道今天要審判的人，卻不知道今天要審理的案件內容。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請各位少安毋躁。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想必沒有人會忘記，一周前的那一天。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#2$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一天發生了太多的事情，食品安全部部長盧比奧的廣播，以及隨之而來的，席捲全城的混亂。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有許多人在那場混亂中喪命，也有許多人對那場混亂感到恐慌。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所幸，這場混亂最後得到了平息。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，許多人已經知道，引起這場混亂的，正是同樣在這場混亂中殞命的貝納爾多·貝洛內本人。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，他的目的，他的動機，卻始終是一個謎。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在那次事件中，有另外一個人也扮演了重要的角色。那個人，正是貝納爾多·貝洛內之子，萊昂圖索·貝洛內。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把人帶上來。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "channel": "a", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安靜。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在場的各位，有的可能第一次見到我，有的可能早就知道我了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是做一個自我介紹吧，我叫萊昂圖索·貝洛內，現在只是一個普通人。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "普通人？你不是貝洛內家族的少爺嗎？", "name": "陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經是，而現在，我已經不再屬於任何家族。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你們有很多疑問，我會一一解釋，不過，首先應當讓各位瞭解，父親到底做了什麼，事情又為何會走到今天這一步。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切，恐怕要從建設部部長卡拉奇之死說起......", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站在法庭中央，眾目睽睽之下，萊昂圖索卻沒有絲毫緊張。"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有條不紊地從那場刺殺開始敘述，將這次事情的全貌向所有人展現。"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g11_mansionhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於新城市的歸屬，各個家族那邊，看起來已經收到了消息。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。“新的移動城市不允許任何家族介入。”", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她願意壓制住其他家族，足以證明，在那場對話中，她並沒有欺騙我們。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，從我瞭解的情況來看，她既沒有說新的移動城市將交給誰管理，也沒有說明理由。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "灰廳的運轉向來如此。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西西里夫人不需要解釋一切，她的命令總是絕對的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們需要。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，關於新城市的一切正鬧得滿城風雨，我們必須給所有人一個交代。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，這也是我們眼前的第一個難題。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切來得太突然了，難道我要做個演講，告訴他們，“我們將要打造一座沒有家族的城市”？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣只會把所有人都嚇跑。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的城市中，如果只有你，我，切利尼娜，還有那些相信盧比奧的官員們存在，那我們在第一步就失敗了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜，西西里夫人也想看看，我們會怎麼解決這個問題吧。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你看起來已經有想法了。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想請你逮捕我，拉維妮婭。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#4$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親的所作所為，無論其中蘊含著他怎樣的思緒，終究是引起了如此大的混亂。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要有人給所有人一個交代。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我的所作所為也是一樣的，不是嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g3_srccourt", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刺殺卡拉奇的自導自演，與薩盧佐的聯手，對羅塞蒂領袖的刺殺，以及最後啟動次級核心區的分離程式。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一件事都不是秘密，但是，當人們得知這背後的推手竟是貝納爾多時，還是引得法庭內部驚呼連連。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索盡可能客觀地，以他所掌握的資訊，將父親的計劃和盤托出。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，在經過了長達一個小時的敘述後，故事終於抵達了尾聲。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你們之中有不少人代表各個家族而來，我猜，你們也已經聽到了一些風聲。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個傳言是對的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切都是我父親的手筆，而他之所以要這麼做，為的正是——", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“一個沒有家族的敘拉古”。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "channel": "a", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個家族的領袖，卻是那個想要毀滅所有家族的人，這怎麼可能！", "name": "疑惑的旁聽官員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，就算是我這個做兒子的，在瞭解到這一切的時候，也是震驚的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個想法，在父親的心中扎根了數十年，直到現在，終於開花結果。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索，別裝了。你的父親已經死了，而你還活著，所以你才想用這種鬼話來為自己脫罪吧。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，新城市的歸屬，我們一清二楚。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我並不介意被代表家族的人這樣指責，只要這樣能夠讓你們滿意。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這一切的幕後黑手是他，為什麼他也死了？", "name": "疑惑的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狼之主。"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索幾乎要脫口而出，最終卻還是壓回心中。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為，與狼之主有關的一切都是那麼荒謬可笑。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親認為，如果家族不應存在，那麼，自己也是應該被清除的對象。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，他在做完一切之後，選擇了自盡。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這真是我聽過的最可笑的笑話！", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道想說，他是一個無私的人？他做這一切，是為了所有敘拉古的普通人？", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......恰恰相反。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認為父親是自私的，他的所作所為，皆是為了他記憶中一幅名為敘拉古的畫卷。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，父親失敗了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原來如此，我明白了。", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，我就說，為什麼貝納爾多死了，你卻還活著。", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然不知道你用了什麼方法，但你恐怕阻止了你的父親，然後拿這件事向西西里夫人邀功。", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你才能夠從西西里夫人那裡獲得新城市的管理權，然後站在這裡堂而皇之地講著故事，試圖為自己博取一些同情。", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說的沒錯吧，弑父者？", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索深吸了一口氣，最終卻只是挪開視線，沒有反駁。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在內心深處，他無法否認這一點。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧啊，他心虛了！", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一個疑問。", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使我們相信這樣的無稽之談，但是，拉維妮婭法官，這和今天的審判有什麼關係？", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道我們要對一個死人的作為下達判決，還要為他的罪行進行量刑？", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為萊昂圖索並不是作為一個證人，為了給各位講一些與他父親有關的事情，並討論其所作所為而站在這裡。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天要審理的案件，事實上是關於新城市的歸屬。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索擅自決定了這座新城市，以及敘拉古未來的事情。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索，就請你講述一下，西西里夫人為什麼會選擇你吧。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這件事情中，是父親的協助者，卻又是阻止父親的人。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我瞭解了這一切之後，我選擇了阻止我的父親。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認為父親是錯誤的，他的作為是無法為敘拉古開闢新時代的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將所有家族都拖入鬥爭，即使家族最後真的不復存在，也不意味著，人們會選擇新的生活。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，在那之上，我認為這確實是一個機會。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，在事件的最後，我來到了西西里夫人面前並向她提出，我要向敘拉古借一座城市。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“一座沒有家族存在的城市”。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "channel": "a", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開什麼玩笑，西西里夫人怎麼可能會同意你的請求！", "name": "易怒的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這並不是一次請求，而是我對敘拉古發起的一次挑戰。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親選擇的方法對西西里夫人來說是在破壞規則，這是她不能容忍的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我選擇的方法......雖然我並不想這麼說，但它卻是西西里夫人可以允許的，否則，我連站在這裡發言的機會都不會有。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索看向一個方向，那裡，站著一名薩科塔神父。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神父戴著眼罩，似乎並沒有關注正在進行的庭審。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，如果是這樣的話，西西里夫人下達的命令，是說得通的......", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，甚至應該說，只有這種說法才能解釋，為什麼西西里夫人會做出那樣的決定。", "name": "敏銳的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果這是真的，萊昂圖索，你今天的所作所為，無疑只是一場作秀。", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審判？你站在這裡，不過只是在向我們宣告，你將是這座新城市的所有者而已，不是嗎？", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這座城市並不屬於我。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的城市將會正常地引入它應有的一切，除了一樣東西——“家族”。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的以為你阻止得了？", "name": "沉著的家族陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是個愚蠢的問題，就好像我問你，家族與普通人的邊界真的被尊重過嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家族願意遵守西西里夫人定下的規矩，只是因為西西里夫人足夠強大。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而所謂家族之間的心照不宣，也只是因為沒有足夠的力量吞掉對方。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們當然會來的，我知道。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，這一次你們會知道，你們曾經小看了什麼東西。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我也歡迎想要做出改變的家族與新城市合作。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“沒有家族的城市”，和“沒有家族的敘拉古”，我覺得沒有什麼區別，都是妄想罷了。", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說它們是妄想，是因為不切實際，還是說難以實現？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當然是不切實際。", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親的做法無疑是錯誤的，但我並不認為這兩者是不切實際的想法。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是眼下的一切讓我們覺得理所當然，所以你才會覺得不切實際。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家族在這片土地上根深蒂固，你是不可能把它們連根拔起的，沒有人做得到。", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但家族可以被改變，他們同樣可以變得更文明。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果家族無法被消滅，那麼本就應當讓它們變成別的東西，只要它們變成的東西，是我們想要的，那就是好的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你真的覺得，你能成功？", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我或許會失敗，但是，難道你不覺得，這其中有嘗試的價值嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "冷靜的市民陪審員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所爭取到的，無非是一種西西里夫人的施捨。", "name": "認真的旁聽官員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家族依然存在，一切看似搖搖欲墜，卻絕沒有那麼容易傾塌。", "name": "認真的旁聽官員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天你的所作所為是作秀也好，認真的也好，都是因為西西里夫人允許，才能夠進行。", "name": "認真的旁聽官員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切，真的存在意義嗎？", "name": "認真的旁聽官員"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......悲哀的是，如果這一切不這麼發生，那麼，恐怕我們只會如同桌布一樣被換掉。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不認為自己的成功是必然的，說實話，那天，我甚至做好了死在那裡的準備。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這並不意味著，當機會出現在我面前時，我不會去把握，哪怕那確實是一種施捨。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許在任何其他地方，發生同樣的事，當事人都可以以更為高潔的態度，對這種施捨作出否定並拒絕。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但在敘拉古，在敘拉古的此時此刻，事情如果只能這樣發生，那我願意接受。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不到萬不得已，盧比奧部長又豈會選擇使用那種方法，不是嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g11_mansionhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道這會引起什麼後果嗎？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在做的，是前所未有的事，我又怎麼能判斷會有怎樣的後果？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我是這麼想的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭，我不僅欠整個沃爾西尼一個交代，我也欠你，以及你身邊的人一個交代，不是嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那天之後，我們並沒有仔細聊過，只是隱約知道彼此的想法。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們真的走在同一條道路上嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想要的新城市，真的與你想要的一致嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們彼此之間其實並不知道對方的想法，不是嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我相信你。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你相信我，那就更應該審判我。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅是為了你，也是為了那些因為盧比奧而聚集在你身邊的官員們。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則，他們憑什麼要相信我，一個前家族少爺？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你沒必要一個人承擔這麼多的。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應該和你站在一起。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，我現在深刻理解了你說的那些話，拉維妮婭。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的立場是不同的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有辦法以一個家族少爺的身份，對你的遭遇和處境感同身受。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我要忍受的，只是卸下這個身份所必須承受的東西罷了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我們從功利的角度來說，市民們信任你，這也是一個絕好的，為你樹立形象的機會。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果你要這麼說，那恐怕也有許多人會把這場審判當做一種作秀吧。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使被這麼認為也沒有關係。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕被認為是一場作秀，有的時候，願意作秀同樣是一種姿態，不是嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是這麼想的，拉維妮婭。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們並沒有在做一件多麼偉大的事。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一天，我們之間也會互相猜忌。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一天，等我們回過神來，或許會發現，把一切搞砸的反而是我們。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是——", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g3_srccourt", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索·貝洛內，是什麼讓你如此堅定地站在這裡？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為一個出身家族的人，你卻在此時此刻，成為了最為反對家族的人，為什麼？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼呢......我也時常在問自己這個問題。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我追求效率的想法？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是被某個追求正義的人的理想所影響？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是耳濡目染了某個值得敬佩的長官的所作所為？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是從家族變遷的一點觀察中得出的結論？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許這些都是原因。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而把這些原因全都歸結到一起，我們或許可以得出一個結論——", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時候到了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許卡拉奇部長躲過了那場刺殺，順利當上建設部部長，他會為相似的目標而努力。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許盧比奧部長選擇了繼續隱忍，穩坐建設部部長的位置，他也會暗中籠絡有志之士，為了改變敘拉古而奮鬥。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並沒有蓄謀已久，我甚至只是在某時某刻突然醒悟，然後僥倖走到了這一步。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我死了，也還會有下一個，下下個人出現。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這一切從來都不意味著我有多麼努力或者多麼獨特，而只是意味著——", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敘拉古到了改變的時候。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個又一個的問題不斷地拋向萊昂圖索，對他的質疑聲和謾駡聲充斥著整個法庭。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他站在法庭中央，認真地，不厭其煩地回答著每一個在他看來有價值的問題。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逐漸地，越來越多的人感受到，這個青年想了很多，並且——"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是認真的。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，整個法院裡的氣勢，竟似乎被他一個人壓了過去。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位到場的陪審員，旁聽的市民，以及透過各種媒體觀看的市民們。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到現在，我的心中依然是忐忑的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我向西西里夫人借來了這座城市，但我卻從沒有認為這座城市屬於我。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是為了將來共同建造這座新城市的你們，為了讓家族這一存在真正從敘拉古被淘汰而努力的你們，向西西里夫人借了這座城市。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我認為我是需要被你們審判的，因為我替你們做出了決定。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，就讓我在這裡說一句大話吧——", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的敘拉古，無權審判我。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為，能夠審判我的，同樣只有你們。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們將獲得這個權力，就好像，你們將獲得打造新城市的權力一樣。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定，未來的某一刻，決定敘拉古未來的權力，也會在你們的手上呢。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的城市，歡迎所有對家族抱有不滿，抱有疑問，或者對我有所質疑的人加入。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想說的，就這些。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這場審判，被認為是萊昂圖索作為新沃爾西尼市長候補的第一次公開演講，引起了廣泛的討論以及一些家族的強烈反抗。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但毫無疑問，這場近乎個人秀的審判，最終為新沃爾西尼的真正運轉，奠定了諸多基礎。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一切才剛剛開始。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}